<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.2">
<l>poṉṉai māmaṇi yaiyaṇi yārntatōr</l>
<l>miṉṉai vēṅkaṭat tucciyiṟ kaṇṭupōy</l>
<l>eṉṉai yāḷuṭai yīcaṉai yempirāṉ</l>
<l>taṉṉai yāmceṉṟu kāṇṭumtaṇ kāvilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone and seen on the peak of Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>Lightning filled with beauty, gold, a great jewel,</l>
<l>Īśa who possess me as [his] servant, our lord,</l>
<l>We will go see [him] in Taṇkā.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
